or other materials in this repository.

### Bitnami MongoDB Helm chart

The MongoDB subchart under `5g/helm-charts/free5gc/charts/mongodb/` is derived
from the Bitnami MongoDB Helm chart (Apache License 2.0), as used in the
towards5gs-helm free5GC packaging.

